Consistency vs Availability Trade-offs

Strong consistency: Use quorum reads/writes (W + R > N)
Eventual consistency: Async replication, last-write-wins
Scaling Strategies

Horizontal: Add more shards
Vertical: Increase memory per node
Read scaling: Add replicas
